@Chris
When I was in high school, snarf meant to laugh so hard while drinking a beverage that liquid came out of your nose. Is there any other term for this?

As teenage boys, we used to actively try to make each other snarf by saying something funny when someone took a drink. Ah, how we passed the time before smart phones.

@Francis

